            <title>[MAHOUT-746] Refactoring of the parallel Naive Bayes implementation in org.apache.mahout.classifier.naivebayes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-746</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I refactored the code in org.apache.mahout.classifier.naivebayes to extend AbstractJob, decoupled the model serialization from the job output, extracted trainer classes and tried to clarify naming and reduce code complexity. I also added tests for the training M/R code as well as a toy integration test.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It would be great if someone could review my patch to make sure I didn&apos;t break anything.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
